# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# secrets: never commit real credentials. Add new secret files above their
# matching pattern here rather than tracking them. Placeholder ".example"/
# ".sample" files ARE allowed (negated below) so devs know what to provide.
# CI (gitleaks) enforces this regardless of local setup.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
